    <h3 id="positioning">
        Positioning
    </h3>
    <p>Based on a simple
        <code>$space</code> variable, and a set of helper classes, positioning your elements with padding or extra margin is as easy as adding a
        class. In this case,
        <code>$space</code> is equal to
        <code>1em</code>.</p>
    
